g.text: 返回 "秒杀未开始或已结束"
从 Redis 读取库存 (stockKey = "seckill:stock:" + voucherId)
检查 Redis Set 是否存在 userId (usersKey = "seckill:users:" + voucherId)
执行 Redis 原子减库存 (DECR stockKey)
向 Redis Set 添加用户 (SADD usersKey, userId)
生成全局唯一订单ID (orderId = redisIdWorker.nextId("order"))
封装秒杀消息 (orderId, userId, voucherId, shopId)
提取 orderId, userId, voucherId, shopId
检查数据库是否已存在 (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tb_voucher_order WHERE user_id = userId AND voucher_id = voucherId)
执行乐观锁库存扣减 (UPDATE tb_seckill_voucher SET stock = stock - 1 WHERE voucher_id = voucherId AND stock > 0)
插入订单到 tb_voucher_order (orderId, userId, voucherId, shopId)
